    <title>Socioeconomic Status and Employee Well-Being: An Intersectional and Resource-Based View of Health Inequalities at Work</title>
    <updated>2025-02-12T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Kelly P. Gabriel, Maira E. Ezerins, Christopher C. Rosen, Allison S. Gabriel, Charmi Patel, Grace J. H. Lim</name>
