    <title>Born to behave: Home CEOs and financial misconduct*</title>
    <updated>2025-02-08T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Zicheng Lei, Dimitris Petmezas, P. Raghavendra Rau, Chen Yang</name>
